        "TileImage": "$($repository 246c1a0b-5ce5-4125-808c-8d38e364b407).Image",
        "Description": "Welcome to the Petronas Towers, 47. Your primary target is hacker Charlie Sidjan. Having aquired an advanced piece of missile technology, he plans to sell it off to the highest bidder. But first, to reach him, you&apos;ll have to take out the hotel&apos;s chief of security, to lower the protection the target will have during the party that will be taking place this night. Additionally, one of the buyers, Vlad Volodin, plans to present a deal to Charlie this night. Keep it from changing hands any more.",
